messages.msgSnippet: She really got into the chapter about various old wives tales mom did you hold an egg over my mouth when I was born, cause if you did, I would talk
messages.messageBody:
She really got into the chapter about various "old wives tales"

"mom did you hold an egg over my mouth when I was born, cause if you
did, I would talk early--that's Germany."

Mom did you wear your clothing too tight, cause that's why I'm a girl...

Yes, blessingways would be nice. This is an old book I bought just
about 11 years ago, when my sister was pg with Alan, before I heard of
things like blessingways, homeschooling, breastfeeding,e tc.

Joylyn
